'''The Ellstree Bar''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] located on the main street of downtown [[New Hope Settlement]] on [[Ladarra]]. Drinks included cold [[Lum/Legends|lum]], and [[Droid/Legends|droids]] were welcome as proclaimed on its [[repliwood]] entrance sign.

Despite its appearance of being deserted, the bar was home to the last generation of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] failed colony of mostly [[Human/Legends|Humans]]. [[Rivo Xarran]] became known as "The Storyteller," as he would gather the children round and tell tales from the past, his own included, when he retired to the world in an attempt to flee [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]].

